  <summary>3/3/1988--Introduced.
Amends the Federal criminal code, with respect to criminal penalties for operating a common carrier under the influence of alcohol or drugs, to: (1) provide criminal penalties for operation of a locomotive under the influence of alcohol or drugs; and (2) provide increased criminal penalties where a death or serious injury results from such operation.</summary>
